1
00:00:01.919 --> 00:00:07.477 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> Station Log, Stardate 47182.1.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>DS9 has been temporarily evacuated</i></c.bg_transparent>

2
00:00:07.556 --> 00:00:10.956 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>due to a violent plasma disruption.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Until the disturbance ends,</i></c.bg_transparent>

3
00:00:11.362 --> 00:00:13.795 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>we'll be forced to maintain the station</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>with a skeleton crew.</i></c.bg_transparent>

4
00:00:14.274 --> 00:00:16.634 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How are we holding up?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-So far, so good.</c.bg_transparent>

5
00:00:16.714 --> 00:00:19.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll say one thing for the Cardassians,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they built this place to last.</c.bg_transparent>

6
00:00:19.393 --> 00:00:20.593 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just in case it doesn't...</c.bg_transparent>

7
00:00:20.992 --> 00:00:24.151 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've got the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Orinoco</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>prepped and ready at Pad C.</c.bg_transparent>

8
00:00:24.232 --> 00:00:25.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Any word from Chief O'Brien?</c.bg_transparent>

9
00:00:25.592 --> 00:00:27.713 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He and Odo checked in about an hour ago.</c.bg_transparent>

10
00:00:27.150 --> 00:00:29.430 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They sealed off the airlocks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the upper and lower pylons</c.bg_transparent>

11
00:00:29.510 --> 00:00:31.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and were moving on to the docking ring.</c.bg_transparent>

12
00:00:31.829 --> 00:00:33.789 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Sisko to O'Brien.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-O'Brien here.</i></c.bg_transparent>

13
00:00:34.290 --> 00:00:36.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What's your status, Chief?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Almost done, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>

14
00:00:37.468 --> 00:00:40.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've sealed all the airlocks</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>on levels 21, 22, and 23.</c.bg_transparent>

15
00:00:41.306 --> 00:00:42.627 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We still have to check the outer bulkheads</c.bg_transparent>

16
00:00:42.706 --> 00:00:44.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>to make sure there hasn't been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any crystallization</c.bg_transparent>

17
00:00:44.906 --> 00:00:46.945 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>from the plasma discharges.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>It shouldn't take too long.</i></c.bg_transparent>

18
00:00:47.304 --> 00:00:48.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>O'Brien out.</c.bg_transparent>

19
00:00:50.344 --> 00:00:51.544 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( faint banging )</c.bg_transparent>

20
00:00:52.904 --> 00:00:54.263 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Did you hear that?</c.bg_transparent>

21
00:00:55.228 --> 00:00:55.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hear what?</c.bg_transparent>

22
00:00:55.903 --> 00:00:57.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I could have sworn I heard something.</c.bg_transparent>

23
00:01:02.140 --> 00:01:03.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Quark!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What are you doing here?</c.bg_transparent>

24
00:01:03.940 --> 00:01:06.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>ODO: You're under strict orders from Sisko</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to stay in the bar.</c.bg_transparent>

25
00:01:07.179 --> 00:01:10.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not a prisoner, Odo.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I volunteered to stay</c.bg_transparent>

26
00:01:10.498 --> 00:01:11.938 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and help you protect the station.</c.bg_transparent>

27
00:01:12.580 --> 00:01:15.167 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The only reason you volunteered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is because there wasn't enough room</c.bg_transparent>

28
00:01:15.972 --> 00:01:19.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>on the evacuation shuttles</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for 600 bars of gold-pressed latinum</c.bg_transparent>

29
00:01:19.255 --> 00:01:20.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>which still doesn't explain</c.bg_transparent>

30
00:01:20.695 --> 00:01:23.134 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>what you're doing out here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the docking ring.</c.bg_transparent>

31
00:01:24.974 --> 00:01:27.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was saying good-bye to my brother.</c.bg_transparent>

32
00:01:27.612 --> 00:01:31.292 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your brother?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>His shuttle left three hours ago.</c.bg_transparent>

33
00:01:32.211 --> 00:01:36.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Funny... it's only been three hours</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm already lost without him.</c.bg_transparent>

34
00:01:36.850 --> 00:01:38.329 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, please!</c.bg_transparent>

35
00:01:38.489 --> 00:01:40.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't try to tell me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you've been sitting out here</c.bg_transparent>

36
00:01:40.369 --> 00:01:42.529 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>all this time pining for Rom.</c.bg_transparent>

37
00:01:43.848 --> 00:01:44.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know, I know.</c.bg_transparent>

38
00:01:45.128 --> 00:01:47.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He couldn't find a cup of water</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if you dropped him in a lake,</c.bg_transparent>

39
00:01:47.727 --> 00:01:51.966 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but even if he is an idiot,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he's still my brother.</c.bg_transparent>

40
00:01:52.325 --> 00:01:55.884 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And you'd betray him in a second</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>if it suited your interests.</c.bg_transparent>

41
00:01:56.804 --> 00:01:58.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That doesn't mean I don't love him.</c.bg_transparent>

42
00:01:58.603 --> 00:01:59.404 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( Odo scoffs )</c.bg_transparent>

43
00:02:00.436 --> 00:02:04.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Chief, do you have any brothers?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-As a matter of fact, I have two.</c.bg_transparent>

44
00:02:05.229 --> 00:02:07.281 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And did you ever have</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to say good-bye to them?</c.bg_transparent>

45
00:02:07.361 --> 00:02:10.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Sure, when I joined Starfleet.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-And did it bring a tear to your eye?</c.bg_transparent>

46
00:02:12.959 --> 00:02:13.958 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I suppose so.</c.bg_transparent>

47
00:02:14.199 --> 00:02:17.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, try explaining that to him.</c.bg_transparent>

48
00:04:24.400 --> 00:04:26.599 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>The storm's intensity is up 37%.</c.bg_transparent>

49
00:04:26.679 --> 00:04:28.478 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is there any way of telling</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how long it'll last?</c.bg_transparent>

50
00:04:28.559 --> 00:04:32.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your guess is as good as mine.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Plasma storms are extremely rare.</c.bg_transparent>

51
00:04:32.398 --> 00:04:33.837 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>But look on the bright side.</c.bg_transparent>

52
00:04:33.917 --> 00:04:35.716 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>This gives us a great</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>opportunity to study one.</c.bg_transparent>

53
00:04:35.957 --> 00:04:36.796 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, lucky us.</c.bg_transparent>

54
00:04:36.956 --> 00:04:38.635 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>You should see the view</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the Promenade.</c.bg_transparent>

55
00:04:38.716 --> 00:04:39.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's simply amazing.</c.bg_transparent>

56
00:04:39.995 --> 00:04:43.748 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I assume the Promenade is secure.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Oh, yes, sir. I've struck the sails</c.bg_transparent>

57
00:04:43.154 --> 00:04:44.714 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>and battened the hatches, so to speak.</c.bg_transparent>

58
00:04:45.345 --> 00:04:47.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: Benjamin,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you better take a look at this.</c.bg_transparent>

59
00:04:48.232 --> 00:04:50.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>( console beeping insistently )</c.bg_transparent>

60
00:04:51.472 --> 00:04:54.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm detecting a small vessel</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>headed this way at one quarter impulse.</c.bg_transparent>

61
00:04:55.470 --> 00:04:57.350 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>-KIRA: They're hailing us.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-On screen.</c.bg_transparent>

62
00:04:59.509 --> 00:05:00.749 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't get a visual.</c.bg_transparent>

63
00:05:01.149 --> 00:05:03.188 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAN: ( static )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>This is the Cargo Ship </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>Ekina.</c.bg_transparent>

64
00:05:03.548 --> 00:05:05.108 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We've been caught by the storm.</i></c.bg_transparent>

65
00:05:05.268 --> 00:05:07.867 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Our engines have been severely damaged.</i></c.bg_transparent>

66
00:05:08.274 --> 00:05:11.306 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>We need emergency assistance.</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>Can you read me?</i></c.bg_transparent>

67
00:05:11.385 --> 00:05:13.825 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:10.00% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Repeat, this is the Cargo Ship </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>Ekina</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>...</i></c.bg_transparent>

68
00:05:15.465 --> 00:05:16.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've lost it.</c.bg_transparent>

69
00:05:17.784 --> 00:05:19.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can we get a transporter lock on the crew?</c.bg_transparent>

70
00:05:21.102 --> 00:05:22.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, there's too much interference.</c.bg_transparent>

71
00:05:23.222 --> 00:05:26.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Engage the tractor beam.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Bring them in to the closest docking bay.</c.bg_transparent>

72
00:05:26.781 --> 00:05:28.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There might be casualties.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll get down to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

73
00:05:28.820 --> 00:05:29.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Good idea.</c.bg_transparent>

74
00:05:30.580 --> 00:05:33.192 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Sisko to O'Brien.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>-</i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>O'Brien here.</c.bg_transparent>

75
00:05:33.140 --> 00:05:36.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>Chief, we've got some storm victims</i></c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent><i>coming in to Docking Bay Five</i></c.bg_transparent>

76
00:05:36.579 --> 00:05:37.697 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent><i>who may be in need of assistance.</i></c.bg_transparent>

77
00:05:38.338 --> 00:05:39.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have to release the emergency seal</c.bg_transparent>

78
00:05:39.858 --> 00:05:41.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>on the airlock before</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they can board the station.</c.bg_transparent>

79
00:05:41.617 --> 00:05:42.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>On my way.</c.bg_transparent>

80
00:05:54.533 --> 00:05:54.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stand clear.</c.bg_transparent>

81
00:05:59.172 --> 00:06:00.291 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( coughing )</c.bg_transparent>

82
00:06:01.290 --> 00:06:02.611 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you all right? Is anyone hurt?</c.bg_transparent>

83
00:06:03.502 --> 00:06:03.890 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KLINGON: Not yet.</c.bg_transparent>

84
00:06:04.610 --> 00:06:06.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What the hell do you think you're doing?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No questions.</c.bg_transparent>

85
00:06:07.609 --> 00:06:10.288 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is a nice way to show your gratitude.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>We just saved your lives out there.</c.bg_transparent>

86
00:06:10.448 --> 00:06:13.807 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You see? The ever-helpful Federation.</c.bg_transparent>

87
00:06:14.607 --> 00:06:16.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-So predictable.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Listen, friend</c.bg_transparent>

88
00:06:16.607 --> 00:06:17.886 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>in case you haven't heard</c.bg_transparent>

89
00:06:18.206 --> 00:06:20.445 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>the Federation and the Klingon</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Empire are allies now.</c.bg_transparent>

90
00:06:20.605 --> 00:06:21.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( spits )</c.bg_transparent>

91
00:06:21.964 --> 00:06:23.450 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Empire is governed</c.bg_transparent>

92
00:06:23.124 --> 00:06:26.163 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>by doddering fools</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and frightened old women</c.bg_transparent>

93
00:06:26.243 --> 00:06:28.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>who aren't worthy of the name "Klingon."</c.bg_transparent>

94
00:06:29.763 --> 00:06:31.561 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mareel! The combadge.</c.bg_transparent>

95
00:06:33.721 --> 00:06:37.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-This one must be the shape-shifter.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Go on! What are you waiting for?</c.bg_transparent>

96
00:06:45.157 --> 00:06:46.277 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're a Trill.</c.bg_transparent>

97
00:06:50.236 --> 00:06:52.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You! Shifter! Inside.</c.bg_transparent>

98
00:06:54.555 --> 00:06:55.994 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And what if I refuse?</c.bg_transparent>

99
00:06:56.914 --> 00:07:00.153 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, do as he says</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and no one will get hurt.</c.bg_transparent>

100
00:07:00.912 --> 00:07:04.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KLINGON: Now! Or this one dies.</c.bg_transparent>

101
00:07:26.865 --> 00:07:28.255 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let's go...</c.bg_transparent>

102
00:07:28.105 --> 00:07:29.464 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ally.</c.bg_transparent>

103
00:07:35.782 --> 00:07:37.222 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Chief, were there any casualties?</c.bg_transparent>

104
00:07:37.302 --> 00:07:39.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That depends on you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-BASHIR: What's this all about?</c.bg_transparent>

105
00:07:39.781 --> 00:07:40.621 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

106
00:07:40.701 --> 00:07:42.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeto, get the Ferengi.</c.bg_transparent>

107
00:07:43.380 --> 00:07:45.939 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Any more questions?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Don't hurt him.</c.bg_transparent>

108
00:07:46.939 --> 00:07:48.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mareel! The box.</c.bg_transparent>

109
00:07:50.138 --> 00:07:55.177 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Put it in your stasis chamber.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Now, or I will destroy it.</c.bg_transparent>

110
00:07:55.977 --> 00:07:57.496 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is that supposed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to be some kind of threat?</c.bg_transparent>

111
00:07:58.136 --> 00:07:59.416 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They've got Odo in there.</c.bg_transparent>

112
00:08:01.534 --> 00:08:05.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see... Well, in that case...</c.bg_transparent>

113
00:08:18.730 --> 00:08:21.916 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm still not getting a response</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from O'Brien or Odo.</c.bg_transparent>

114
00:08:21.369 --> 00:08:22.808 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Run a level-3 security scan.</c.bg_transparent>

115
00:08:23.608 --> 00:08:24.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KLINGON: Don't bother.</c.bg_transparent>

116
00:08:27.247 --> 00:08:30.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please, take your hands</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>away from the controls.</c.bg_transparent>

117
00:08:32.565 --> 00:08:33.365 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now!</c.bg_transparent>

118
00:08:35.165 --> 00:08:36.644 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get to the center of the room.</c.bg_transparent>

119
00:08:40.403 --> 00:08:41.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do as he says.</c.bg_transparent>

120
00:08:49.939 --> 00:08:51.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't worry, Verad.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It's going to be all right.</c.bg_transparent>

121
00:09:07.835 --> 00:09:09.915 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get with the others. Move!</c.bg_transparent>

122
00:09:12.593 --> 00:09:14.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your turn, little man.</c.bg_transparent>

123
00:09:20.231 --> 00:09:23.150 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't forget to disable the backups</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>as well as the primary systems.</c.bg_transparent>

124
00:09:27.869 --> 00:09:30.708 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's my fault, Commander.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They caught us by surprise.</c.bg_transparent>

125
00:09:31.467 --> 00:09:34.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Somehow, they must have neutralized</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the security systems</c.bg_transparent>

126
00:09:34.547 --> 00:09:36.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-in the docking ring.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-How did they manage that?</c.bg_transparent>

127
00:09:36.946 --> 00:09:39.145 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not sure but I've got</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>a pretty good idea.</c.bg_transparent>

128
00:09:39.626 --> 00:09:42.665 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We ran across Quark</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in an airlock a little while ago.</c.bg_transparent>

129
00:09:43.544 --> 00:09:46.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When this is over Quark</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I are going to have a little talk.</c.bg_transparent>

130
00:09:55.300 --> 00:09:56.580 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you know him?</c.bg_transparent>

131
00:10:10.936 --> 00:10:12.335 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah, Yeto.</c.bg_transparent>

132
00:10:13.256 --> 00:10:15.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's such a pleasure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>doing business with Klingons.</c.bg_transparent>

133
00:10:15.894 --> 00:10:18.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're so, um... punctual.</c.bg_transparent>

134
00:10:19.893 --> 00:10:23.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I see your ship was rescued</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>according to plan.</c.bg_transparent>

135
00:10:23.332 --> 00:10:25.891 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Um, I've got your merchandise right here</c.bg_transparent>

136
00:10:26.812 --> 00:10:29.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-but I don't see any latinum.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You Ferengi!</c.bg_transparent>

137
00:10:29.571 --> 00:10:32.690 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You think you're so clever,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but you're stupid.</c.bg_transparent>

138
00:10:32.769 --> 00:10:35.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, now, there's no need</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for name-calling.</c.bg_transparent>

139
00:10:36.289 --> 00:10:38.487 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you don't want</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>these liquid data chains,</c.bg_transparent>

140
00:10:38.888 --> 00:10:41.247 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure I can line up</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>dozens of other buyers.</c.bg_transparent>

141
00:10:41.366 --> 00:10:42.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go right ahead.</c.bg_transparent>

142
00:10:43.687 --> 00:10:44.486 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeto,</c.bg_transparent>

143
00:10:44.606 --> 00:10:47.455 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you expect me to believe</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you've come all this way,</c.bg_transparent>

144
00:10:47.605 --> 00:10:51.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>braved the storm, just to tell me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that the deal is off?</c.bg_transparent>

145
00:10:51.724 --> 00:10:52.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stupid Ferengi!</c.bg_transparent>

146
00:10:53.483 --> 00:10:54.682 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling nervously )</c.bg_transparent>

147
00:10:56.402 --> 00:10:59.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I said no one moves.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm Commander of this station.</c.bg_transparent>

148
00:10:59.801 --> 00:11:03.113 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What is your business here?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You'll have to ask my employer.</c.bg_transparent>

149
00:11:07.639 --> 00:11:13.517 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm... I'm sorry about all this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>If everyone would just cooperate</c.bg_transparent>

150
00:11:13.597 --> 00:11:17.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I promise it will all be over soon.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What will be over soon?</c.bg_transparent>

151
00:11:17.476 --> 00:11:20.555 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>QUARK: This is an outrage!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I demand to be released at once!</c.bg_transparent>

152
00:11:20.675 --> 00:11:22.554 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Enough of your whining!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Who are these people?</c.bg_transparent>

153
00:11:22.634 --> 00:11:23.674 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What do they want from us?</c.bg_transparent>

154
00:11:23.754 --> 00:11:26.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Funny. I was about</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to ask you that question.</c.bg_transparent>

155
00:11:26.353 --> 00:11:28.332 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-That's enough.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-SISKO: I agree.</c.bg_transparent>

156
00:11:28.112 --> 00:11:29.313 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now tell me what you want here.</c.bg_transparent>

157
00:11:32.831 --> 00:11:33.631 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

158
00:11:35.351 --> 00:11:37.590 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... want Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

159
00:11:39.109 --> 00:11:43.189 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-She's not going anywhere with you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No, no. I don't want the girl.</c.bg_transparent>

160
00:11:43.268 --> 00:11:49.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I only want what is rightfully mine...</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>What should have been mine years ago.</c.bg_transparent>

161
00:11:53.186 --> 00:11:54.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

162
00:11:55.944 --> 00:12:00.423 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: The symbiont, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He's come to steal my symbiont.</c.bg_transparent>

163
00:12:10.700 --> 00:12:14.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You can't remove Jadzia's symbiont.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>If you do, she'll die.</c.bg_transparent>

164
00:12:15.591 --> 00:12:16.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He knows that, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

165
00:12:17.984 --> 00:12:17.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm...</c.bg_transparent>

166
00:12:18.818 --> 00:12:23.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry about all this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Please, believe me,</c.bg_transparent>

167
00:12:23.337 --> 00:12:27.953 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I wish I didn't have to do this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Then don't.</c.bg_transparent>

168
00:12:28.614 --> 00:12:29.775 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't have a choice.</c.bg_transparent>

169
00:12:31.540 --> 00:12:35.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... spent my whole life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>trying to qualify for the joining.</c.bg_transparent>

170
00:12:35.973 --> 00:12:41.851 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... studied constantly,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>every day, every waking hour.</c.bg_transparent>

171
00:12:43.911 --> 00:12:46.489 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I sacrificed... everything,</c.bg_transparent>

172
00:12:46.609 --> 00:12:50.369 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and then I went before</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the symbiosis evaluation board</c.bg_transparent>

173
00:12:50.448 --> 00:12:51.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And...</c.bg_transparent>

174
00:12:52.767 --> 00:12:57.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They reduced my entire life to one word...</c.bg_transparent>

175
00:12:58.726 --> 00:13:00.845 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Unsuitable.</c.bg_transparent>

176
00:13:01.805 --> 00:13:03.764 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's nothing to be ashamed of.</c.bg_transparent>

177
00:13:04.244 --> 00:13:07.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Neither of my parents</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or my sister underwent symbiosis,</c.bg_transparent>

178
00:13:08.243 --> 00:13:10.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and they live happy</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and productive lives.</c.bg_transparent>

179
00:13:10.722 --> 00:13:13.481 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Only one Trill in ten</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is chosen to be joined.</c.bg_transparent>

180
00:13:14.139 --> 00:13:16.160 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's easy for you to say.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They chose you.</c.bg_transparent>

181
00:13:16.880 --> 00:13:18.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I was one of the lucky ones.</c.bg_transparent>

182
00:13:18.840 --> 00:13:20.479 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now it's Verad's time to be lucky.</c.bg_transparent>

183
00:13:21.159 --> 00:13:22.239 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>KIRA: Why Dax?</c.bg_transparent>

184
00:13:22.839 --> 00:13:25.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are thousands</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of symbionts on Trill. Why her?</c.bg_transparent>

185
00:13:25.958 --> 00:13:27.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I did research. I worked it all out.</c.bg_transparent>

186
00:13:28.157 --> 00:13:31.768 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Dax symbiont is the best match for me.</c.bg_transparent>

187
00:13:31.156 --> 00:13:33.995 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We have mutual interests,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>science, diplomacy--</c.bg_transparent>

188
00:13:34.155 --> 00:13:37.594 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad, there is another reason,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>isn't there?</c.bg_transparent>

189
00:13:38.314 --> 00:13:39.233 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: The wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

190
00:13:40.593 --> 00:13:41.993 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>After you've stolen the symbiont</c.bg_transparent>

191
00:13:42.727 --> 00:13:44.312 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>you plan on escaping</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Gamma Quadrant, don't you?</c.bg_transparent>

192
00:13:44.472 --> 00:13:46.751 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Can you think of a better place</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to start a new life?</c.bg_transparent>

193
00:13:46.951 --> 00:13:50.670 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I understand your frustration</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but there could be dozens of reasons</c.bg_transparent>

194
00:13:50.750 --> 00:13:52.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>why the board</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>didn't select you for symbiosis.</c.bg_transparent>

195
00:13:53.389 --> 00:13:55.293 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>They have to be very careful.</c.bg_transparent>

196
00:13:55.788 --> 00:13:59.428 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>An improper joining</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>can cause permanent psychological damage</c.bg_transparent>

197
00:13:59.827 --> 00:14:02.187 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to both the symbiont and the host.</c.bg_transparent>

198
00:14:03.186 --> 00:14:05.146 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>They were only looking</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>after your best interests.</c.bg_transparent>

199
00:14:05.626 --> 00:14:07.705 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Your best interests maybe, but not mine.</c.bg_transparent>

200
00:14:08.465 --> 00:14:13.543 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All they've done is condemn me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to a life of... of...</c.bg_transparent>

201
00:14:15.863 --> 00:14:16.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mediocrity.</c.bg_transparent>

202
00:14:16.902 --> 00:14:18.622 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, I refuse to accept that.</c.bg_transparent>

203
00:14:18.701 --> 00:14:22.100 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I--I'm not going to spend</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the rest of my life dreaming</c.bg_transparent>

204
00:14:22.540 --> 00:14:26.620 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>about what I could have been.</c.bg_transparent>

205
00:14:27.539 --> 00:14:32.857 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What I should have been.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I deserve... more...</c.bg_transparent>

206
00:14:33.937 --> 00:14:38.256 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-and I'm going to get it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Yeto, T'Kar, it's time.</c.bg_transparent>

207
00:14:41.159 --> 00:14:42.655 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll have no part in this.</c.bg_transparent>

208
00:14:44.542 --> 00:14:45.853 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... I understand.</c.bg_transparent>

209
00:14:46.573 --> 00:14:47.453 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groans )</c.bg_transparent>

210
00:14:50.852 --> 00:14:51.772 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasping )</c.bg_transparent>

211
00:14:51.851 --> 00:14:53.931 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>VERAD: Keep away from him, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

212
00:14:57.170 --> 00:14:59.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There, you see? I've taken the first step.</c.bg_transparent>

213
00:15:02.448 --> 00:15:04.928 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Even if I don't get what I want,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>my life is over,</c.bg_transparent>

214
00:15:05.876 --> 00:15:09.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>so either you help me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or you and your friends will die.</c.bg_transparent>

215
00:15:09.406 --> 00:15:10.526 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's your choice.</c.bg_transparent>

216
00:15:12.246 --> 00:15:13.460 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll help.</c.bg_transparent>

217
00:15:14.325 --> 00:15:16.564 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want anyone else hurt</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>because of me.</c.bg_transparent>

218
00:15:18.842 --> 00:15:21.723 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But you have to give me your word</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that no one else on this station</c.bg_transparent>

219
00:15:21.803 --> 00:15:22.923 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>will be harmed.</c.bg_transparent>

220
00:15:23.265 --> 00:15:24.802 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I... I promise.</c.bg_transparent>

221
00:15:25.721 --> 00:15:26.522 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>

222
00:15:29.521 --> 00:15:31.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do as he says, Julian, please.</c.bg_transparent>

223
00:15:41.557 --> 00:15:43.676 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Let me treat</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Chief O'Brien's phaser wound first.</c.bg_transparent>

224
00:15:43.996 --> 00:15:45.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: It won't take long.</c.bg_transparent>

225
00:15:45.635 --> 00:15:47.675 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There's an emergency</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>medical kit in the console.</c.bg_transparent>

226
00:15:49.955 --> 00:15:50.754 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Get it!</c.bg_transparent>

227
00:15:56.872 --> 00:15:57.792 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hold still, Chief.</c.bg_transparent>

228
00:16:00.911 --> 00:16:02.391 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

229
00:16:07.549 --> 00:16:08.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There.</c.bg_transparent>

230
00:16:08.508 --> 00:16:10.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There should be no permanent damage.</c.bg_transparent>

231
00:16:13.227 --> 00:16:16.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Apply this every 20 minutes or so.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It should help the wound regenerate.</c.bg_transparent>

232
00:16:16.946 --> 00:16:17.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Enough stalling!</c.bg_transparent>

233
00:16:18.785 --> 00:16:21.545 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do as he says, Doctor.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>This is no time to be a hero.</c.bg_transparent>

234
00:16:22.265 --> 00:16:23.584 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take them to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

235
00:16:25.424 --> 00:16:27.703 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This isn't over, Dax. I promise you.</c.bg_transparent>

236
00:16:27.983 --> 00:16:28.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: Dax...</c.bg_transparent>

237
00:16:31.821 --> 00:16:32.901 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>DAX: I know, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

238
00:16:33.941 --> 00:16:36.861 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll do everything you can.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>And just in case it isn't enough,</c.bg_transparent>

239
00:16:38.340 --> 00:16:39.659 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want you to know it's been fun.</c.bg_transparent>

240
00:16:42.419 --> 00:16:43.538 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAREEL: Let's go.</c.bg_transparent>

241
00:16:50.216 --> 00:16:51.162 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good luck.</c.bg_transparent>

242
00:16:51.416 --> 00:16:57.574 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It won't be long now, and then you'll see.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Everything will be just as I promised.</c.bg_transparent>

243
00:16:59.294 --> 00:17:00.253 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know.</c.bg_transparent>

244
00:17:15.169 --> 00:17:17.128 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What's that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-BASHIR: It's a delta wave inducer</c.bg_transparent>

245
00:17:17.288 --> 00:17:18.967 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>to keep you asleep during the operation.</c.bg_transparent>

246
00:17:19.407 --> 00:17:21.727 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It also increases</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>your body's natural endorphin production</c.bg_transparent>

247
00:17:21.807 --> 00:17:24.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-to help accelerate the healing process.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I don't want it.</c.bg_transparent>

248
00:17:24.486 --> 00:17:26.125 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I strongly recommend that you use it.</c.bg_transparent>

249
00:17:26.206 --> 00:17:28.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The surgery</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>will be much easier on you if--</c.bg_transparent>

250
00:17:28.365 --> 00:17:30.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want your advice.</c.bg_transparent>

251
00:17:32.244 --> 00:17:33.523 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I want to be awake.</c.bg_transparent>

252
00:17:34.163 --> 00:17:38.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Use a neuroelectrical suppresser</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and set up a monitor</c.bg_transparent>

253
00:17:38.242 --> 00:17:39.801 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>so that I can watch the procedure.</c.bg_transparent>

254
00:17:40.521 --> 00:17:42.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That way, if you run into any trouble</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I can assist you.</c.bg_transparent>

255
00:17:44.600 --> 00:17:46.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, let's get started.</c.bg_transparent>

256
00:17:54.837 --> 00:17:56.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry, Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

257
00:18:02.754 --> 00:18:07.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't blame yourself, Julian.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You did everything you could.</c.bg_transparent>

258
00:18:07.553 --> 00:18:08.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I...</c.bg_transparent>

259
00:18:11.712 --> 00:18:12.991 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This will help you sleep.</c.bg_transparent>

260
00:18:14.311 --> 00:18:15.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

261
00:18:24.188 --> 00:18:25.228 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Forgive me.</c.bg_transparent>

262
00:18:33.257 --> 00:18:34.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>How long can Dax survive</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>without the symbiont?</c.bg_transparent>

263
00:18:35.344 --> 00:18:38.864 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Once the symbiont is removed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the host usually dies within hours</c.bg_transparent>

264
00:18:39.903 --> 00:18:43.582 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but Jadzia is young and healthy.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Bashir will do what he can.</c.bg_transparent>

265
00:18:45.341 --> 00:18:48.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-She'll make it through the night.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That still doesn't give us much time.</c.bg_transparent>

266
00:18:49.608 --> 00:18:49.981 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No talking!</c.bg_transparent>

267
00:18:50.608 --> 00:18:50.940 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No!</c.bg_transparent>

268
00:19:04.164 --> 00:19:05.296 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( hissing )</c.bg_transparent>

269
00:19:05.655 --> 00:19:07.154 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( loud grunting )</c.bg_transparent>

270
00:19:09.654 --> 00:19:10.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

271
00:19:12.574 --> 00:19:14.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to kill you,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Commander, but I will!</c.bg_transparent>

272
00:20:50.864 --> 00:20:51.784 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is ridiculous.</c.bg_transparent>

273
00:20:52.824 --> 00:20:54.503 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you realize</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they're going to kill us?</c.bg_transparent>

274
00:20:56.103 --> 00:20:57.902 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What are you people sitting around for?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Do something.</c.bg_transparent>

275
00:20:58.342 --> 00:20:59.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you have any suggestions?</c.bg_transparent>

276
00:21:00.861 --> 00:21:04.207 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why should I have any suggestions?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not the military mastermind.</c.bg_transparent>

277
00:21:04.540 --> 00:21:06.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm just a victim of circumstances.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Victim? Really?</c.bg_transparent>

278
00:21:07.379 --> 00:21:09.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then maybe you'd like to tell me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how four armed terrorists</c.bg_transparent>

279
00:21:09.978 --> 00:21:11.858 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>got by our docking ring security grid.</c.bg_transparent>

280
00:21:11.938 --> 00:21:13.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Security grid?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know anything about...</c.bg_transparent>

281
00:21:13.417 --> 00:21:16.456 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Save it, Quark.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You crossed the line this time.</c.bg_transparent>

282
00:21:18.136 --> 00:21:21.952 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You sold us out</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and now Dax may die because of it.</c.bg_transparent>

283
00:21:21.216 --> 00:21:24.215 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, whatever happens next,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>one thing is certain you are through here.</c.bg_transparent>

284
00:21:24.294 --> 00:21:25.854 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( snarls )</c.bg_transparent>

285
00:21:36.330 --> 00:21:38.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Are you all right?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'll live.</c.bg_transparent>

286
00:21:39.104 --> 00:21:41.249 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't try that again.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I don't want to have to hurt anyone.</c.bg_transparent>

287
00:21:41.569 --> 00:21:43.409 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Tell that to Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

288
00:21:44.248 --> 00:21:45.408 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's different.</c.bg_transparent>

289
00:21:47.487 --> 00:21:48.447 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Do you really believe that?</c.bg_transparent>

290
00:21:49.127 --> 00:21:51.126 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You heard Verad.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>They didn't leave him any other choice.</c.bg_transparent>

291
00:21:51.486 --> 00:21:55.405 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-No, that's his reason. What's yours?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I owe him.</c.bg_transparent>

292
00:21:56.604 --> 00:21:58.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I grew up on the streets of Khefka IV.</c.bg_transparent>

293
00:21:58.404 --> 00:22:00.284 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I never would have made it out of there</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>without Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

294
00:22:00.723 --> 00:22:02.443 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What was he doing on Khefka IV?</c.bg_transparent>

295
00:22:03.403 --> 00:22:06.122 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He was the communications clerk</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>at the Federation Consulate.</c.bg_transparent>

296
00:22:06.201 --> 00:22:08.761 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He used to visit</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the accommodation house where I worked.</c.bg_transparent>

297
00:22:10.160 --> 00:22:11.520 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I used to help him relax.</c.bg_transparent>

298
00:22:13.319 --> 00:22:15.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>When he was recalled to Trill,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he asked me to go with him.</c.bg_transparent>

299
00:22:16.394 --> 00:22:19.384 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-We've been together ever since.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-And that's it?</c.bg_transparent>

300
00:22:20.374 --> 00:22:24.364 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He got you out of a bad situation</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and now you're willing to kill for him?</c.bg_transparent>

301
00:22:24.396 --> 00:22:25.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I owe him my life.</c.bg_transparent>

302
00:22:27.115 --> 00:22:29.354 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If there's anything</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I can do for him I'll do it.</c.bg_transparent>

303
00:22:30.114 --> 00:22:31.794 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Even if it means losing him?</c.bg_transparent>

304
00:22:33.793 --> 00:22:34.673 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Losing him?</c.bg_transparent>

305
00:22:36.193 --> 00:22:40.111 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>After the surgery Verad</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>won't be just Verad anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

306
00:22:40.951 --> 00:22:44.270 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll be a blending of Verad, Dax,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and all the previous hosts,</c.bg_transparent>

307
00:22:44.790 --> 00:22:48.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>their memories, their knowledge,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>even their personalities.</c.bg_transparent>

308
00:22:49.788 --> 00:22:51.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad told me</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that you'd say things like that.</c.bg_transparent>

309
00:22:53.427 --> 00:22:54.467 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know he'll change.</c.bg_transparent>

310
00:22:54.867 --> 00:22:57.271 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll be smarter, more confident,</c.bg_transparent>

311
00:22:57.106 --> 00:22:59.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but in all the important ways,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>he'll be the same.</c.bg_transparent>

312
00:22:59.545 --> 00:23:01.905 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sorry,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but if he told you that, he's lying.</c.bg_transparent>

313
00:23:02.585 --> 00:23:06.184 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Once a Trill</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>is joined it's like a rebirth.</c.bg_transparent>

314
00:23:06.783 --> 00:23:08.702 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll be an entirely different person.</c.bg_transparent>

315
00:23:08.862 --> 00:23:11.102 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you think</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'm going to betray Verad, you're wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

316
00:23:12.262 --> 00:23:15.541 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It doesn't matter</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>what you say. I love him,</c.bg_transparent>

317
00:23:16.580 --> 00:23:19.299 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>and I'm going to stand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>by him no matter what.</c.bg_transparent>

318
00:23:20.219 --> 00:23:21.419 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>VERAD: I never doubted it.</c.bg_transparent>

319
00:23:24.338 --> 00:23:25.338 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

320
00:23:29.296 --> 00:23:31.964 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, not just Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

321
00:23:31.856 --> 00:23:33.336 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm Verad Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

322
00:24:01.607 --> 00:24:02.446 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Take this.</c.bg_transparent>

323
00:24:03.207 --> 00:24:06.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come on, we haven't got much time.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Just move it back and forth over the wound</c.bg_transparent>

324
00:24:06.126 --> 00:24:07.885 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-in slow, even strokes.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Why bother?</c.bg_transparent>

325
00:24:08.458 --> 00:24:09.925 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>She'll be dead in a few hours anyway.</c.bg_transparent>

326
00:24:10.204 --> 00:24:12.841 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not if I have anything to do with it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Now, help me.</c.bg_transparent>

327
00:24:12.244 --> 00:24:13.124 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why should I?</c.bg_transparent>

328
00:24:13.563 --> 00:24:16.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She let herself be slaughtered</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>like a mindless </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>t'gla.</i></c.bg_transparent>

329
00:24:17.428 --> 00:24:19.402 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If she wanted to live,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>she should have fought back.</c.bg_transparent>

330
00:24:19.921 --> 00:24:22.161 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She did what she did</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to save the rest of us.</c.bg_transparent>

331
00:24:22.361 --> 00:24:25.440 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then she is a fool,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and she deserves her fate.</c.bg_transparent>

332
00:24:25.759 --> 00:24:27.159 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now listen to me, Yeto,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or whatever your name is.</c.bg_transparent>

333
00:24:27.279 --> 00:24:28.319 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't give a damn</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>about your warrior ethic</c.bg_transparent>

334
00:24:28.399 --> 00:24:29.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or your Klingon philosophy.</c.bg_transparent>

335
00:24:29.519 --> 00:24:31.198 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This woman is dying,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and I need your help to save her.</c.bg_transparent>

336
00:24:31.398 --> 00:24:32.678 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, take this instrument.</c.bg_transparent>

337
00:24:33.518 --> 00:24:37.556 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well... so the little human</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>has some spark after all.</c.bg_transparent>

338
00:24:49.993 --> 00:24:52.152 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping erratically )</c.bg_transparent>

339
00:24:52.992 --> 00:24:56.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come on. Come on.</c.bg_transparent>

340
00:24:59.190 --> 00:25:01.309 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping steadies )</c.bg_transparent>

341
00:25:07.587 --> 00:25:08.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

342
00:25:09.676 --> 00:25:13.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, thank God. I thought I'd lost you.</c.bg_transparent>

343
00:25:13.986 --> 00:25:15.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The symbiont.</c.bg_transparent>

344
00:25:18.184 --> 00:25:18.984 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's gone.</c.bg_transparent>

345
00:25:19.645 --> 00:25:23.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Oh, everything went perfectly.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The operation was a complete success.</c.bg_transparent>

346
00:25:25.462 --> 00:25:26.742 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I feel so alone.</c.bg_transparent>

347
00:25:28.212 --> 00:25:29.780 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I've got you stabilized.</c.bg_transparent>

348
00:25:31.420 --> 00:25:33.699 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If only we could get the symbiont</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>back in time.</c.bg_transparent>

349
00:25:35.259 --> 00:25:36.459 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm scared, Julian.</c.bg_transparent>

350
00:25:38.258 --> 00:25:41.137 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not going to die. Do you hear me?</c.bg_transparent>

351
00:25:43.457 --> 00:25:44.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not going to let you die.</c.bg_transparent>

352
00:25:45.563 --> 00:25:49.414 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>( shallow breathing )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I've never felt so empty.</c.bg_transparent>

353
00:25:53.543 --> 00:25:54.493 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: Just rest.</c.bg_transparent>

354
00:25:56.692 --> 00:25:57.492 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax?</c.bg_transparent>

355
00:25:59.772 --> 00:26:01.211 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

356
00:26:03.512 --> 00:26:03.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's me.</c.bg_transparent>

357
00:26:04.850 --> 00:26:10.648 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Curzon, Tobin, Jadzia, all the others,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>they're all a part of you now.</c.bg_transparent>

358
00:26:10.728 --> 00:26:15.785 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's amazing.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>So many ideas. So many memories.</c.bg_transparent>

359
00:26:15.647 --> 00:26:19.461 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eight lifetimes of memories.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It must be incredible.</c.bg_transparent>

360
00:26:19.165 --> 00:26:21.581 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's better than I ever imagined.</c.bg_transparent>

361
00:26:21.445 --> 00:26:23.524 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The station must look very different</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to you now.</c.bg_transparent>

362
00:26:23.645 --> 00:26:27.484 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It does. I... I know this place.</c.bg_transparent>

363
00:26:29.123 --> 00:26:31.842 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( chuckling ) And I know you, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

364
00:26:33.721 --> 00:26:35.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Of course you do.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Remember when we first met?</c.bg_transparent>

365
00:26:35.761 --> 00:26:37.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Pelios Station.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Anastasia?</c.bg_transparent>

366
00:26:37.720 --> 00:26:39.879 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And that trip we took</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Cliffs of Bole?</c.bg_transparent>

367
00:26:39.960 --> 00:26:41.639 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( both men laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

368
00:26:42.598 --> 00:26:44.598 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: All the months we served</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>aboard the </c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i>Livingston.</i></c.bg_transparent>

369
00:26:44.678 --> 00:26:47.238 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And Science Officer Kustanovich.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>What was it?</c.bg_transparent>

370
00:26:47.317 --> 00:26:49.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Eight helpings of Andorian Redbat?</c.bg_transparent>

371
00:26:49.476 --> 00:26:51.516 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( laughing )</c.bg_transparent>

372
00:26:52.755 --> 00:26:55.358 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO: I don't think I've ever seen</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>someone eat so much.</c.bg_transparent>

373
00:26:55.555 --> 00:26:58.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Remember my wedding?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I remember your bachelor party,</c.bg_transparent>

374
00:26:58.394 --> 00:26:59.593 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>or some of it anyway.</c.bg_transparent>

375
00:27:02.730 --> 00:27:04.352 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>And the time we discovered the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

376
00:27:05.672 --> 00:27:06.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My, my, my.</c.bg_transparent>

377
00:27:09.431 --> 00:27:10.951 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>One of Jadzia's proudest moments.</c.bg_transparent>

378
00:27:11.830 --> 00:27:14.110 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>And now that woman is bleeding to death</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>in the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

379
00:27:14.549 --> 00:27:18.348 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I'd rather not discuss that, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You have to discuss it, Dax.</c.bg_transparent>

380
00:27:19.286 --> 00:27:20.948 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know as well as I do</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>we can't let her die.</c.bg_transparent>

381
00:27:21.276 --> 00:27:23.387 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>She's not going to die.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>She'll live on in me.</c.bg_transparent>

382
00:27:23.947 --> 00:27:25.826 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jadzia's memories will live on,</c.bg_transparent>

383
00:27:26.465 --> 00:27:29.865 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but Jadzia herself will die,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and you'll have killed her.</c.bg_transparent>

384
00:27:29.944 --> 00:27:33.264 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You think I don't know that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll never be able to forget it,</c.bg_transparent>

385
00:27:34.783 --> 00:27:37.862 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but I promise you, Benjamin</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>I'll do all I can to make up for it.</c.bg_transparent>

386
00:27:37.942 --> 00:27:39.941 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not going</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to the Gamma Quadrant to hide.</c.bg_transparent>

387
00:27:40.501 --> 00:27:44.860 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>There are entire worlds who can benefit</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from my knowledge and experience.</c.bg_transparent>

388
00:27:45.204 --> 00:27:48.779 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I can help them, and I will.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I have a better idea.</c.bg_transparent>

389
00:27:48.859 --> 00:27:51.458 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-VERAD: What's that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Help Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

390
00:27:52.538 --> 00:27:56.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come with me down to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Put the symbiont back where it belongs.</c.bg_transparent>

391
00:27:57.697 --> 00:28:00.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't do that, Benjamin,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>even if I wanted to.</c.bg_transparent>

392
00:28:00.375 --> 00:28:03.814 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you see? It's too late.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The integration is already underway.</c.bg_transparent>

393
00:28:04.214 --> 00:28:07.653 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But there's still time to stop it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Jadzia's life can still be saved.</c.bg_transparent>

394
00:28:07.733 --> 00:28:10.173 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't listen to him.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>He's just trying to confuse you.</c.bg_transparent>

395
00:28:10.252 --> 00:28:11.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all right, Mareel.</c.bg_transparent>

396
00:28:11.852 --> 00:28:15.112 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Benjamin, the symbiont is still weak</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>from the operation.</c.bg_transparent>

397
00:28:15.917 --> 00:28:19.610 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If we attempt another joining so soon,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>it might not survive.</c.bg_transparent>

398
00:28:20.504 --> 00:28:22.609 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-VERAD: Are you willing to risk that?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I am.</c.bg_transparent>

399
00:28:24.208 --> 00:28:26.647 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The question is, are you?</c.bg_transparent>

400
00:28:27.247 --> 00:28:29.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Why are you wasting your time with him?</c.bg_transparent>

401
00:28:29.447 --> 00:28:30.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because he's my friend!</c.bg_transparent>

402
00:28:31.366 --> 00:28:32.926 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now, go watch the others.</c.bg_transparent>

403
00:28:37.924 --> 00:28:40.283 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>We are still friends, aren't we, Benjamin?</c.bg_transparent>

404
00:28:41.397 --> 00:28:41.803 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I hope so.</c.bg_transparent>

405
00:28:43.603 --> 00:28:45.322 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Come with me down to the Infirmary</c.bg_transparent>

406
00:28:45.402 --> 00:28:46.202 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and prove it.</c.bg_transparent>

407
00:28:48.761 --> 00:28:49.921 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't do that.</c.bg_transparent>

408
00:28:54.239 --> 00:29:00.437 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then you're not the Dax that I know.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Our friendship is over.</c.bg_transparent>

409
00:29:28.298 --> 00:29:30.691 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Here, drink this.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What is it?</c.bg_transparent>

410
00:29:31.691 --> 00:29:33.707 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Senarian egg broth.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It'll keep your strength up.</c.bg_transparent>

411
00:29:35.347 --> 00:29:37.706 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right, don't drink it.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>It makes no difference to me.</c.bg_transparent>

412
00:29:37.986 --> 00:29:38.786 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hold on.</c.bg_transparent>

413
00:29:39.946 --> 00:29:40.946 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you.</c.bg_transparent>

414
00:29:51.223 --> 00:29:52.982 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He even looks different, doesn't he?</c.bg_transparent>

415
00:29:54.141 --> 00:29:57.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The way he stands,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the way he moves, talks.</c.bg_transparent>

416
00:29:57.820 --> 00:30:01.179 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-He's better than he was.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm glad you think so.</c.bg_transparent>

417
00:30:02.991 --> 00:30:02.898 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I do.</c.bg_transparent>

418
00:30:03.458 --> 00:30:06.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Really? The way he dismissed you before?</c.bg_transparent>

419
00:30:06.578 --> 00:30:09.537 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Verad never did that.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-He's under a lot of stress.</c.bg_transparent>

420
00:30:09.697 --> 00:30:12.816 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>SISKO:</c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent><i> </i></c.bg_transparent><c.bg_transparent>Verad was under stress</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the minute he stepped onto this station,</c.bg_transparent>

421
00:30:13.576 --> 00:30:15.815 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-but he never turned on you, did he?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What's your point, Commander?</c.bg_transparent>

422
00:30:15.975 --> 00:30:16.855 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I think you know.</c.bg_transparent>

423
00:30:17.774 --> 00:30:19.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're trying to turn me against Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

424
00:30:19.694 --> 00:30:22.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad no longer exists.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know that better than I do.</c.bg_transparent>

425
00:30:22.973 --> 00:30:25.252 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right, then.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Verad Dax, but it won't work.</c.bg_transparent>

426
00:30:26.211 --> 00:30:29.251 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Nothing has changed between us.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You really believe that?</c.bg_transparent>

427
00:30:29.691 --> 00:30:30.490 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes.</c.bg_transparent>

428
00:30:32.809 --> 00:30:33.850 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right.</c.bg_transparent>

429
00:30:35.529 --> 00:30:36.969 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Then make me believe it.</c.bg_transparent>

430
00:30:37.488 --> 00:30:39.968 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Go in there and talk to him.</c.bg_transparent>

431
00:30:41.247 --> 00:30:42.687 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Talk to him about what?</c.bg_transparent>

432
00:30:43.475 --> 00:30:44.567 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't know. Whatever you want.</c.bg_transparent>

433
00:30:44.726 --> 00:30:47.525 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm sure the two of you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have a lot to say to one another.</c.bg_transparent>

434
00:30:51.521 --> 00:30:53.444 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I don't want to disturb him.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Why not?</c.bg_transparent>

435
00:30:53.564 --> 00:30:54.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Because I don't want to!</c.bg_transparent>

436
00:30:55.483 --> 00:30:57.563 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, look at him,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>sitting in there all alone.</c.bg_transparent>

437
00:30:57.843 --> 00:30:59.681 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-He needs you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's enough.</c.bg_transparent>

438
00:30:59.922 --> 00:31:02.121 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't understand</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>why you're being so reluctant.</c.bg_transparent>

439
00:31:02.201 --> 00:31:04.441 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is the perfect time</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for the two of you to get reacquainted.</c.bg_transparent>

440
00:31:04.520 --> 00:31:06.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I said that's enough!</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-VERAD: Mareel.</c.bg_transparent>

441
00:31:09.393 --> 00:31:09.999 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Is anything wrong?</c.bg_transparent>

442
00:31:10.279 --> 00:31:11.918 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, everything's fine.</c.bg_transparent>

443
00:31:12.878 --> 00:31:13.677 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good.</c.bg_transparent>

444
00:31:15.556 --> 00:31:16.357 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Be careful.</c.bg_transparent>

445
00:31:17.197 --> 00:31:19.116 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wouldn't want anything to happen to you.</c.bg_transparent>

446
00:31:35.791 --> 00:31:37.351 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunting and groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

447
00:31:38.350 --> 00:31:40.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I got him! I got him!</c.bg_transparent>

448
00:31:41.149 --> 00:31:42.389 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( roaring )</c.bg_transparent>

449
00:31:43.291 --> 00:31:43.909 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stay back.</c.bg_transparent>

450
00:31:44.428 --> 00:31:46.683 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

451
00:31:47.667 --> 00:31:49.586 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Maybe we should talk about this, huh?</c.bg_transparent>

452
00:31:50.386 --> 00:31:51.426 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( grunts )</c.bg_transparent>

453
00:31:54.305 --> 00:31:55.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>My ear.</c.bg_transparent>

454
00:31:56.105 --> 00:31:57.704 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

455
00:32:00.983 --> 00:32:01.863 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Pathetic.</c.bg_transparent>

456
00:32:02.823 --> 00:32:05.382 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mareel, take him to the Infirmary.</c.bg_transparent>

457
00:32:05.822 --> 00:32:07.342 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

458
00:32:16.779 --> 00:32:18.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-( screaming )</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-What is it now?</c.bg_transparent>

459
00:32:19.897 --> 00:32:21.777 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Please... it hurts.</c.bg_transparent>

460
00:32:22.537 --> 00:32:24.217 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All right. Hold on.</c.bg_transparent>

461
00:32:27.455 --> 00:32:29.334 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The damage</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>appears to be fairly superficial.</c.bg_transparent>

462
00:32:30.495 --> 00:32:31.614 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( whispering ) No.</c.bg_transparent>

463
00:32:32.494 --> 00:32:37.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But Ferengi ears are incredibly sensitive.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>So I'd better run some further tests.</c.bg_transparent>

464
00:32:37.933 --> 00:32:39.519 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( moaning loudly )</c.bg_transparent>

465
00:32:45.250 --> 00:32:47.930 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The storm's intensity's dropped</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>another 20%.</c.bg_transparent>

466
00:32:49.729 --> 00:32:51.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I know this has been</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>hard for you, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

467
00:32:51.608 --> 00:32:54.248 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's been hard for both of us</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>but it's almost over.</c.bg_transparent>

468
00:32:54.567 --> 00:32:55.367 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>MAREEL: Good.</c.bg_transparent>

469
00:32:55.727 --> 00:32:57.766 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm getting tired of waiting here.</c.bg_transparent>

470
00:33:00.246 --> 00:33:03.604 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How are you feeling?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Better than ever, thanks to you.</c.bg_transparent>

471
00:33:04.964 --> 00:33:06.643 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I couldn't have done this without you.</c.bg_transparent>

472
00:33:07.244 --> 00:33:10.722 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I would have spent the rest</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of my life a mediocre man</c.bg_transparent>

473
00:33:10.802 --> 00:33:12.641 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>only dreaming about what might have been.</c.bg_transparent>

474
00:33:14.522 --> 00:33:15.961 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You know what you have to do.</c.bg_transparent>

475
00:33:16.809 --> 00:33:17.760 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You just worry about getting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>through the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

476
00:33:18.808 --> 00:33:20.240 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The Klingons and I will make sure</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>that no one stops you.</c.bg_transparent>

477
00:33:20.319 --> 00:33:23.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Remember, I don't want you staying here</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>any longer than you have to.</c.bg_transparent>

478
00:33:23.918 --> 00:33:26.385 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Give me an hour,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>then head for the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

479
00:33:26.118 --> 00:33:27.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The runabout's on Pad C.</c.bg_transparent>

480
00:33:27.477 --> 00:33:29.597 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The sooner you leave,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the sooner I can follow</c.bg_transparent>

481
00:33:30.157 --> 00:33:31.476 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and the sooner we'll be together.</c.bg_transparent>

482
00:33:37.754 --> 00:33:39.434 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's going to be all right, isn't it?</c.bg_transparent>

483
00:33:41.433 --> 00:33:43.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just wait for me at the rendezvous point.</c.bg_transparent>

484
00:34:00.348 --> 00:34:01.308 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( loud moaning )</c.bg_transparent>

485
00:34:01.708 --> 00:34:04.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Stop whining</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>or I'll put you out of your misery.</c.bg_transparent>

486
00:34:04.106 --> 00:34:05.466 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's not his fault.</c.bg_transparent>

487
00:34:05.546 --> 00:34:06.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's got a deep contusion</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>of the auricular lobe</c.bg_transparent>

488
00:34:06.985 --> 00:34:08.465 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and a possible dislocated malleus.</c.bg_transparent>

489
00:34:08.585 --> 00:34:11.224 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>In a Ferengi, either condition</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>could be fatal.</c.bg_transparent>

490
00:34:12.464 --> 00:34:14.903 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>But if you want him to stop,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>give me a hand with this.</c.bg_transparent>

491
00:34:15.183 --> 00:34:16.822 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm not your nurse!</c.bg_transparent>

492
00:34:16.942 --> 00:34:20.502 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Look, let's not go through that again.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Just hold this against his ear.</c.bg_transparent>

493
00:34:20.582 --> 00:34:22.501 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( high-pitched whining )</c.bg_transparent>

494
00:34:24.940 --> 00:34:26.139 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( screams )</c.bg_transparent>

495
00:34:26.220 --> 00:34:27.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not too hard.</c.bg_transparent>

496
00:34:29.978 --> 00:34:31.190 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groaning )</c.bg_transparent>

497
00:34:31.986 --> 00:34:32.418 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Just another second.</c.bg_transparent>

498
00:34:35.497 --> 00:34:36.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Relax.</c.bg_transparent>

499
00:34:37.696 --> 00:34:38.896 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( gasps )</c.bg_transparent>

500
00:34:42.955 --> 00:34:42.895 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>There.</c.bg_transparent>

501
00:34:45.214 --> 00:34:47.813 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Thank you, Doctor. I feel better already.</c.bg_transparent>

502
00:34:52.924 --> 00:34:53.132 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>How is she?</c.bg_transparent>

503
00:34:54.251 --> 00:34:55.171 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I have her stabilized</c.bg_transparent>

504
00:34:55.251 --> 00:34:57.290 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but there's no telling</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>how much time she has left.</c.bg_transparent>

505
00:34:58.904 --> 00:35:00.530 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got to get the symbiont</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>back before it's too late.</c.bg_transparent>

506
00:35:01.169 --> 00:35:03.168 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-What are you doing?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Odo's in here.</c.bg_transparent>

507
00:35:03.728 --> 00:35:04.528 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He is?</c.bg_transparent>

508
00:35:04.608 --> 00:35:07.208 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yes, and we've got to get him out.</c.bg_transparent>

509
00:35:07.567 --> 00:35:09.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Are you sure?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-Quark!</c.bg_transparent>

510
00:35:11.872 --> 00:35:12.326 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If only we knew the access code.</c.bg_transparent>

511
00:35:15.206 --> 00:35:16.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Allow me.</c.bg_transparent>

512
00:35:21.763 --> 00:35:24.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping softly )</c.bg_transparent>

513
00:35:29.921 --> 00:35:33.400 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Ah... standard</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>Delgorian locking mechanism.</c.bg_transparent>

514
00:35:33.800 --> 00:35:35.398 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Sophisticated...</c.bg_transparent>

515
00:35:36.519 --> 00:35:38.518 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>but vulnerable if you know its weaknesses.</c.bg_transparent>

516
00:35:38.798 --> 00:35:40.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Hand me that laser scalpel.</c.bg_transparent>

517
00:35:45.396 --> 00:35:46.316 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Uh-huh.</c.bg_transparent>

518
00:35:50.594 --> 00:35:51.395 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mm-hmm.</c.bg_transparent>

519
00:35:51.914 --> 00:35:53.353 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( clicking )</c.bg_transparent>

520
00:35:53.434 --> 00:35:54.873 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( beeping )</c.bg_transparent>

521
00:35:55.513 --> 00:35:56.553 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( lock releases )</c.bg_transparent>

522
00:35:59.272 --> 00:36:00.272 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's a gift.</c.bg_transparent>

523
00:36:02.191 --> 00:36:04.230 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The storm's decreased another 15%.</c.bg_transparent>

524
00:36:04.310 --> 00:36:07.949 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Excellent. That should be more than enough</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to allow safe passage to the wormhole.</c.bg_transparent>

525
00:36:08.789 --> 00:36:09.629 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad to Yeto.</c.bg_transparent>

526
00:36:11.908 --> 00:36:13.507 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad to Yeto.</c.bg_transparent>

527
00:36:14.268 --> 00:36:15.467 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Yeto, report!</c.bg_transparent>

528
00:36:15.587 --> 00:36:17.506 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The doctor must have overpowered him.</c.bg_transparent>

529
00:36:18.146 --> 00:36:20.625 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-The doctor? Impossible.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-It's the shape-shifter.</c.bg_transparent>

530
00:36:20.866 --> 00:36:23.624 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>He must have freed the shape-shifter.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>T'Kar, get me to the ship.</c.bg_transparent>

531
00:36:24.705 --> 00:36:26.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'd better take a hostage just in case.</c.bg_transparent>

532
00:36:27.243 --> 00:36:28.636 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll go with you.</c.bg_transparent>

533
00:36:28.144 --> 00:36:29.942 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>VERAD: I'd love your company, Benjamin,</c.bg_transparent>

534
00:36:30.636 --> 00:36:32.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>but somehow, I don't think you</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>have my best interests at heart.</c.bg_transparent>

535
00:36:33.101 --> 00:36:35.661 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-Kira, I hate to inconvenience you--</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-That's all right.</c.bg_transparent>

536
00:36:35.981 --> 00:36:38.740 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>If Odo's free there's no way</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>you're getting off this station.</c.bg_transparent>

537
00:36:43.419 --> 00:36:44.218 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Mareel?</c.bg_transparent>

538
00:36:45.498 --> 00:36:46.498 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good luck.</c.bg_transparent>

539
00:36:48.737 --> 00:36:50.897 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, Benjamin, I guess this is good-bye.</c.bg_transparent>

540
00:36:51.496 --> 00:36:53.856 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Not many friendships</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>last over two lifetimes.</c.bg_transparent>

541
00:36:55.615 --> 00:36:57.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I wish we could have made it three.</c.bg_transparent>

542
00:36:57.774 --> 00:36:59.654 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You'll be seeing me again, Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

543
00:37:22.927 --> 00:37:23.927 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So...</c.bg_transparent>

544
00:37:25.326 --> 00:37:27.166 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Where's this rendezvous going to be?</c.bg_transparent>

545
00:37:28.765 --> 00:37:32.844 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-You don't really expect me to tell you.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-No, but I hope you like it there,</c.bg_transparent>

546
00:37:32.924 --> 00:37:35.963 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>because you'll be waiting</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>for Verad a long time.</c.bg_transparent>

547
00:37:36.162 --> 00:37:38.962 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-How would you know?</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-You told me yourself.</c.bg_transparent>

548
00:37:40.602 --> 00:37:43.241 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I saw the look on your face</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>when he asked you to wait for him.</c.bg_transparent>

549
00:37:46.400 --> 00:37:48.439 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>The plan was, he was supposed</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to get there first.</c.bg_transparent>

550
00:37:50.792 --> 00:37:52.278 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That he would wait for me,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>not the other way around.</c.bg_transparent>

551
00:37:52.718 --> 00:37:57.637 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Well, maybe it was an honest mistake.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>A slip of the tongue.</c.bg_transparent>

552
00:37:57.836 --> 00:38:00.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No. He lied to me.</c.bg_transparent>

553
00:38:02.754 --> 00:38:04.314 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's never lied to me before.</c.bg_transparent>

554
00:38:06.274 --> 00:38:07.273 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He's not coming.</c.bg_transparent>

555
00:38:09.433 --> 00:38:10.793 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He doesn't need me anymore.</c.bg_transparent>

556
00:38:11.552 --> 00:38:13.512 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>No, you're wrong.</c.bg_transparent>

557
00:38:14.911 --> 00:38:17.511 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He does need you now, more than ever.</c.bg_transparent>

558
00:38:20.150 --> 00:38:21.429 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You never give up, do you?</c.bg_transparent>

559
00:38:22.549 --> 00:38:26.868 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>-I told you, I'm not going to betray him.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>-I'm not asking you to.</c.bg_transparent>

560
00:38:26.948 --> 00:38:29.987 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm asking you to save him,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>to help us save him.</c.bg_transparent>

561
00:38:30.186 --> 00:38:31.906 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>All you care about is Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

562
00:38:31.986 --> 00:38:35.185 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's right, and you care about Verad,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>and we can save them both.</c.bg_transparent>

563
00:38:36.865 --> 00:38:37.904 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't you see?</c.bg_transparent>

564
00:38:39.184 --> 00:38:41.583 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Dax and Verad</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>were never meant to be joined.</c.bg_transparent>

565
00:38:41.703 --> 00:38:44.782 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We've got to remove the symbiont</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>while there's still time.</c.bg_transparent>

566
00:38:49.101 --> 00:38:50.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If you hurt him...</c.bg_transparent>

567
00:38:52.900 --> 00:38:53.700 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll kill you.</c.bg_transparent>

568
00:38:59.978 --> 00:39:01.337 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I don't doubt it.</c.bg_transparent>

569
00:39:24.571 --> 00:39:26.570 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The ship... it's gone.</c.bg_transparent>

570
00:39:26.650 --> 00:39:28.729 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>That's because I released</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>the docking clamps.</c.bg_transparent>

571
00:39:47.443 --> 00:39:49.203 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Looks like that good-bye</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>was a little premature.</c.bg_transparent>

572
00:39:49.643 --> 00:39:52.282 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't be ridiculous.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You're not going to shoot me.</c.bg_transparent>

573
00:39:52.802 --> 00:39:54.521 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>What makes you so sure?</c.bg_transparent>

574
00:39:54.801 --> 00:39:57.361 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>This is Dax you're talking to, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

575
00:39:57.680 --> 00:40:00.920 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>We both know that if you shoot me,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>even on stun,</c.bg_transparent>

576
00:40:00.999 --> 00:40:03.199 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>you risk killing the symbiont.</c.bg_transparent>

577
00:40:03.278 --> 00:40:06.878 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>If I let you go, Jadzia dies.</c.bg_transparent>

578
00:40:06.958 --> 00:40:08.757 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>But Dax will live.</c.bg_transparent>

579
00:40:09.597 --> 00:40:12.196 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>What's one girl's life</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>compared to eight lifetimes</c.bg_transparent>

580
00:40:12.276 --> 00:40:13.876 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>of knowledge and experience?</c.bg_transparent>

581
00:40:16.955 --> 00:40:20.514 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not going to shoot me.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>You know that, and so do I.</c.bg_transparent>

582
00:40:24.432 --> 00:40:25.872 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Good-bye, Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

583
00:40:29.351 --> 00:40:30.191 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

584
00:40:36.868 --> 00:40:39.289 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Don't call me Benjamin.</c.bg_transparent>

585
00:40:39.388 --> 00:40:40.788 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>( groans )</c.bg_transparent>

586
00:41:01.181 --> 00:41:02.181 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I feel strange.</c.bg_transparent>

587
00:41:04.340 --> 00:41:05.221 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So empty.</c.bg_transparent>

588
00:41:05.660 --> 00:41:09.259 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's over now, Verad.</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>The symbiont is back where it belongs.</c.bg_transparent>

589
00:41:11.499 --> 00:41:12.298 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>So close.</c.bg_transparent>

590
00:41:14.938 --> 00:41:16.176 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had it.</c.bg_transparent>

591
00:41:18.136 --> 00:41:19.536 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I had it, and...</c.bg_transparent>

592
00:41:22.951 --> 00:41:23.894 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Now I'm alone.</c.bg_transparent>

593
00:41:25.146 --> 00:41:26.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>You're not alone, Verad.</c.bg_transparent>

594
00:41:27.974 --> 00:41:28.893 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm here.</c.bg_transparent>

595
00:41:30.653 --> 00:41:31.852 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'll always be here.</c.bg_transparent>

596
00:41:34.292 --> 00:41:36.331 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I can't remember any of it.</c.bg_transparent>

597
00:41:40.130 --> 00:41:40.929 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The knowledge...</c.bg_transparent>

598
00:41:43.368 --> 00:41:44.368 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>The confidence...</c.bg_transparent>

599
00:41:47.477 --> 00:41:48.743 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>It's all gone.</c.bg_transparent>

600
00:41:49.727 --> 00:41:50.527 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>BASHIR: Commander?</c.bg_transparent>

601
00:41:57.484 --> 00:41:58.324 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Jadzia.</c.bg_transparent>

602
00:42:03.683 --> 00:42:04.602 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>Are you?</c.bg_transparent>

603
00:42:05.325 --> 00:42:05.922 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I'm fine.</c.bg_transparent>

604
00:42:08.961 --> 00:42:13.919 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:79.33% 
<c.bg_transparent>I remember it all, Benjamin,</c.bg_transparent>
<c.bg_transparent>everything he thought, everything he did,</c.bg_transparent>

605
00:42:15.439 --> 00:42:16.798 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>and it's so sad.</c.bg_transparent>

606
00:42:21.877 --> 00:42:23.374 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>I guess...</c.bg_transparent>

607
00:42:24.756 --> 00:42:26.156 position:50.00%,middle align:middle size:80.00% line:84.67% 
<c.bg_transparent>He'll always be with me.</c.bg_transparent>

